            <div class="news-banner-tag">Fleet Update</div>
            <div class="news-banner-date">Mar 20, 2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="news-card-body">
            <div class="news-card-title">Two New Airbus A321XLR Aircraft Join Our Regional Fleet</div>
            <div class="news-card-excerpt">AviatesAir Regional is pleased to confirm delivery of two A321XLR aircraft, extending our reach to ultra-long thin routes across Asia-Pacific and Europe.</div>
            <div class="news-card-footer">
                <div class="news-author">
                    <div class="avatar-sm">ZH</div>
                    <span class="news-author-name">Zakir Horizontal</span>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="news-read-link">Read
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </a>
